    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876350/extras/204c3e08e804b29ec4df93f5f39a2451.avif?t=1680711029\" width=616 height=248 /></span><br><br>扮演风格迥异的六位史诗英雄，召唤部队、施展法术并摧毁敌方高塔，在这款争锋相对的刺激塔防游戏中勇夺胜利。玩家可以选择在包含三个战役的单人冒险模式中体验不同寻常的故事、动人心弦的美妙乐曲与手工打造的美丽场景，除此以外，玩家们还可以选择与亲朋好友挑战1v1或者2v2的快节奏对抗赛。玩家可以构筑自定义牌组并升级卡牌，创造不可思议的部队与法术组合，竭尽全力打败对手，摧毁为他们提供力量的灵魂宝石并攀登排行榜的顶点。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876350/extras/bd99e73ea20f2be6f9c2b0a8a11c0846.poster.avif?t=1680711029\" width=616 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876350/extras/bd99e73ea20f2be6f9c2b0a8a11c0846.webm?t=1680711029\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876350/extras/bd99e73ea20f2be6f9c2b0a8a11c0846.mp4?t=1680711029\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
